{"tid":1205710,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(借ac)如果中左胡椒噴霧或催淚彈點處理","createTime":"2019-06-11T22:42:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-11T23:30:13.000Z","uid":199286,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e78626940d8ba468aa06bab110be471d812c31fa","tid":1205710,"uid":199286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T22:42:53.000Z","msg":"作為醫科生（mbbs）想分享一下如果野餐中左胡椒噴霧同催淚彈如何處理。雖然我以下講既野好多人都識，但係真係中左睇唔到野抖唔到氣好多人都會慌，所以打遍野提提大家如何急救及幫助身邊既戰友<br />\n<br />\n1.胡椒噴霧和催淚彈均屬類近嘅chemical irritant, 冇解藥，除非嚴重生理反應，否則數小時後會復元<br />\n<br />\n2.生理反應<br />\n- 眼鼻口，呼吸道及感到刺痛<br />\n-皮膚紅腫刺痛甚致起水泡<br />\n-大量流眼水或未能張開眼睛（blepharospasm）<br />\n-氣管收縮，呼吸困難，心跳加速<br />\n-感到噁心，嘔吐<br />\n<br />\n3.自行處理放法<br />\n-即時離開現埸(來日方長，復元後再打過)<br />\n-脫去外衣，並清洗<br />\n-用清水或生理鹽水洗眼。一定要開眼切底洗，如果真係未能開眼請求醫，唔好強行用手打開<br />\n-戴con既除con<br />\n-用水或梘水洗受影響皮膚<br />\n-注意清洗時刺痛可能會加劇<br />\n-嚴重呼吸困難嘅話請立刻求助(999)<br />\n-如過自行處理後仍感到不適，請盡快求醫<br />\n<br />\n最後，當然唔中就最好啦，各位加油<br />\n(第一次出post請各位巴打輕手d)"},{"pid":"dc10c2156d9ddb2ceb9b65fb16a2fbca7e912db8","tid":1205710,"uid":4142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T23:18:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"875ec1006db248c28056c53dc49b013889a2d3bb","tid":1205710,"uid":190714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T23:20:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e1f9f1cb8128cf32ace0875b879d56f7c327cebd","tid":1205710,"uid":245676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T23:21:10.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"f4a3989ab4ee596a264f11223fc43734f36cdcf5","tid":1205710,"uid":190714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T23:22:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db6171b81ab1f31ddca59eda5c4fa545cd65da1c","tid":1205710,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T23:25:59.000Z","msg":"辣椒素脂溶性<br />\n用全脂牛奶洗會否更有效?"},{"pid":"988305ac055adade10aa5ea514aa978572855514","tid":1205710,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T23:27:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://matadornetwork.com/change/how-to-relieve-pepper-spray-burns/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmatadornetwork.com%2Fchange%2Fhow-to-relieve-pepper-spray-burns%2F&d=NC%2FTzFAtl3V7yegmN9swvpgFNMRZLCTiZeA0y1vO9n4%3D&h=96c82c01\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://matadornetwork.com/change/how-to-relieve-pepper-spray-burns/</a>"},{"pid":"623d0e4e5df205e4e8f277dc79e1ae72ce10d31b","tid":1205710,"uid":190714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T23:28:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2734d974229d40923c975413b7afb54d6c493255","tid":1205710,"uid":240930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T23:29:15.000Z","msg":"輕手？落力d推就真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"635890c4f615f713413f0aa68076bec909016960","tid":1205710,"uid":190714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T23:30:13.000Z","msg":"推"}]}